BEGIN_PGML

Zoe is pole-vaulting. At the end of her approach run, she has a horizontal velocity of [`[$v]`] [`m/s`] and her center of gravity is [`[$cog]`] [`m`] high. If Zoe's mass is [`[$m]`] [`kg`], estimate how high she should be able to vault if her kinetic and potential energies are all converted to potential energy.

[`h=`] [_____]{"$h"} [`m`]  

